<div class="card vault-info mb-10 text-center max-w-1000-centered">
  <h1 class="mb-20">Welcome to ZokuVault, <%= current_user.try(:name) %>!</h1>

  <h5 class="mb-20 lh-35 max-w-1000 clr-gray-dark inline-block fw-500">Before we get started, here’s a reminder of what we’re doing everyday to keep your data safe.
  </h5>

   <div class="max-w-800 m-0-auto mb-30">
     <%= image_tag "SVG/data-lock.svg", :class => "w-100 inline-block mt-20"%>
     <p class="description lh-30 clr-gray-dark-tinted w-80-percent text-aligned fr mt-10"><span class="inline-block fw-600">Secure Data Centers</span><br>ZokuVault's physical infrastructure is hosted and managed within secure data centers and utilizes industry-leading technology. Our data center operators continually manage risk and undergo recurring assessments to ensure compliance with industry standards, including ISO 27001, SOC 1 and SOC 2, SSAE 16, and ISAE 3402.</p>
     <span class="clear mb-10"></span>

     <%= image_tag "SVG/key-lock.svg", :class => "w-100 inline-block mt-20"%>
     <p class="description lh-30 clr-gray-dark-tinted w-80-percent text-aligned fr mt-10"><span class="inline-block fw-600">Encrypted Data</span><br>We encrypt all of your data at rest using 256-bit AES encryption, and up to 256-bit encryption in transit based on your browser capabilities.</p>
     <span class="clear mb-10"></span>

     <%= image_tag "SVG/web-lock.svg", :class => "w-100 inline-block mt-20"%>
     <p class="description lh-30 clr-gray-dark-tinted w-80-percent text-aligned fr mt-10"><span class="inline-block fw-600">Zero Knowledge Policy</span><br>ZokuVault employees are unable to see any of the information or documents you keep in your vault without your express permission.</p>
     <span class="clear mb-30"></span>

     <%= link_to 'Next', phone_setup_account_path, class: 'button big-button-2 blue-button m-0-auto' %>
   </div>
</div>
